text: Ismael Ramzi (29 August 1917 - 8 February 1983) was an Egyptian diver. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Egyptian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Egypt Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
